# Gala Node Setup and Status Server

This repository contains scripts for:

1. Setting up the Gala Node software on an Ubuntu Linux VM.
2. Running an HTTP server to return the status of the Gala Node.

## Files

- `setup_gala_node.sh`: Script to install and configure the Gala Node software.
- `status_server.py`: Python script to set up an HTTP server that responds with the Gala Node status.

## Usage

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/gala-node-setup.git


chmod +x bootstrap.sh
./bootstrap.sh
